<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Kerr - McGee Corp.</ENAMEX> said it will spend <ENAMEX TYPE="MONEY">$ 42 million</ENAMEX> to purchase land and relocate its ammonium perchlorate storage facility to <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Clark County</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Nev.</ENAMEX> , from <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Henderson</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Nev</ENAMEX> .
