In <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">May 1988</ENAMEX> , an ammonium perchlorate plant in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Henderson</ENAMEX> owned by an <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">American Pacific Corp.</ENAMEX> unit was leveled by a series of explosions .
